00:35.130 --> 00:37.351
- Hello?
- This is Principal Hudgins

00:37.469 --> 00:39.303
calling from
the White Pine Bay High School

00:39.404 --> 00:40.654
emergency phone tree.

00:40.774 --> 00:43.157
I'm sorry to report
that one of our teachers,

00:43.275 --> 00:46.038
Blaire Watson,
was found dead this morning,

00:46.278 --> 00:48.229
the victim of a violent crime

00:48.330 --> 00:49.897
which is currently
being investigated

00:49.998 --> 00:52.033
by the sheriff's office.

00:52.117 --> 00:55.002
This has been a profound loss
for all of us.

00:55.087 --> 00:57.872
There will be no school Monday
so members of our community

00:57.956 --> 01:00.258
can attend
her memorial service.

01:00.375 --> 01:02.126
We encourage everyone to attend

01:02.244 --> 01:04.411
to celebrate the life
of this wonderful teacher.

01:04.513 --> 01:06.514
What is it?

01:14.273 --> 01:17.108
That was the principal
of your school.

01:18.110 --> 01:20.111
What happened?

01:23.115 --> 01:26.150
Norman...
what happened last night?

01:26.268 --> 01:27.935
You said something
about Miss Watson

01:28.036 --> 01:30.437
was going
to give you a ride home?

01:32.491 --> 01:33.774
- Uh-huh.
- But she didn't?

01:33.876 --> 01:37.245
You never got in the car?

01:37.329 --> 01:39.464
I don't remember.

01:39.581 --> 01:43.117
I just remember running home.

01:47.381 --> 01:48.982
I guess she couldn't
have given me a ride

01:49.007 --> 01:52.093
if I was running home, right?

01:54.563 --> 01:56.564
Why?

02:00.018 --> 02:03.154
Um...
Miss Watson is dead.

02:06.108 --> 02:08.359
What?

02:08.476 --> 02:11.496
Apparently, someone killed her.

02:15.083 --> 02:17.335
Man, who is born of a woman,

02:17.452 --> 02:21.822
has but a short time to live,
and is full of misery.

02:21.924 --> 02:24.825
He comes up and is cut down
like a flower.

02:24.927 --> 02:27.762
In the midst of life,
we are in death.

02:27.846 --> 02:30.431
Of whom may we seek
for our succor, oh lord,

02:30.516 --> 02:34.468
who is justly displeased
because of our sins?

02:34.553 --> 02:37.338
Yet, oh lord God most holy...

02:37.439 --> 02:41.442
Oh lord, most mighty, oh holy
and most merciful savior,

02:41.527 --> 02:44.979
deliver us not into the bitter
pains of eternal death.

02:45.063 --> 02:47.982
Do not shut your merciful ears
to our prayers...

02:54.072 --> 02:56.490
But spare us, lord most holy,

02:56.575 --> 02:59.493
oh, God most mighty,

02:59.578 --> 03:02.330
oh, holy and merciful savior,
most worthy judge eternal.

03:04.082 --> 03:06.367
Suffer us not,
in our last hour,

03:06.468 --> 03:10.004
for any pains of death,
to fall from your grace.

03:22.184 --> 03:25.102
You need to eat something.

03:31.243 --> 03:35.396
She was so kind.

03:35.497 --> 03:39.750
I can't imagine
why anyone would hurt her.

03:39.868 --> 03:41.469
Sweetheart,
you didn't really know her.

03:41.569 --> 03:44.171
You knew only one part of her.

03:44.256 --> 03:47.408
God knows what else was going on
in that woman's life.

03:49.211 --> 03:52.246
We only see the tip of
the iceberg with--with anyone.

03:52.347 --> 03:55.016
We see what people
want us to see, but--

03:55.100 --> 03:56.417
but that doesn't mean

03:56.518 --> 03:57.918
there wasn't something else
underneath.

03:58.020 --> 03:59.612
No, she wasn't a bad person.

03:59.732 --> 04:01.472
No, I'm not saying she was.

04:05.894 --> 04:08.279
- Who would do this to her?
- I don't know, honey.

04:08.397 --> 04:12.483
But it's not your problem
to figure out who, okay?

